trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemStyle"></xref> objects in a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en samling av <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemStyle"> </xref> objekter i en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu"> </xref> kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen kan ikke arves.

trans-unit.source: The MenuItemStyleCollection class is used to store and manage a collection of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemStyle> objects in a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> control.
trans-unit.target: Klassen MenuItemStyleCollection brukes til å lagre og behandle en samling av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemStyle>objekter i en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemStyle>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> control uses the MenuItemStyleCollection class as the underlying data type of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.LevelMenuItemStyles%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.LevelSelectedStyles%2A> properties.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu>kontrollen bruker MenuItemStyleCollection-klassen som underliggende datatypen for det <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.LevelMenuItemStyles%2A>og <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.LevelSelectedStyles%2A>Egenskaper.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.LevelSelectedStyles%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.LevelMenuItemStyles%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.LevelMenuItemStyles%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.LevelSelectedStyles%2A> properties are an alternative to the individual style properties (such as <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.StaticMenuItemStyle%2A>).
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.LevelMenuItemStyles%2A>og <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.LevelSelectedStyles%2A>er et alternativ til individuelle stilegenskaper (eksempel <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.StaticMenuItemStyle%2A>).</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.StaticMenuItemStyle%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.LevelSelectedStyles%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.LevelMenuItemStyles%2A>

trans-unit.source: These properties are applied to regular menu items and the selected menu item, respectively, based on the menu item's level in the menu.
trans-unit.target: Disse egenskapene er brukt på vanlige menyelementer og det valgte menyelementet henholdsvis basert på menyelementene nivå i menyen.

trans-unit.source: The first style in the collection corresponds to the menu item style for the first level of the menu.
trans-unit.target: Den første malen i samlingen samsvarer med stilen for menyelement for det første nivået i listen.

trans-unit.source: The second style in the collection corresponds to the menu item style for the second level of the menu, and so on.
trans-unit.target: Andre stilen i samlingen samsvarer med stilen for menyelement for nivå for meny- og så videre.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.LevelMenuItemStyles%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.LevelSelectedStyles%2A> properties are most often used to generate menus where menu items at a certain level have the same appearance, regardless of whether they have submenus.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.LevelMenuItemStyles%2A>og <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.LevelSelectedStyles%2A>Egenskaper oftest brukes til å generere menyer der menyelementer på et bestemt nivå har samme utseendet, uavhengig om de har undermenyer.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.LevelSelectedStyles%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.LevelMenuItemStyles%2A>

trans-unit.source: The MenuItemStyleCollection class inherits most of its members from the <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection> class.
trans-unit.target: MenuItemStyleCollection klassen arver de fleste av medlemmene fra <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection>klasse.</xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection>

trans-unit.source: For more information on the inherited members, see <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection>.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon om arvede medlemmer, kan du se <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection>.</xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection>
